Package logic

Class UsageVisitingReport

java.lang.Object
logic.UsageVisitingReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UsageVisitingReport extends Object implements Serializable
The UsageVisitingReport class represents a visiting report for usage statistics. This class provides attributes and methods to manage visiting report information such as time range, full/enter counter, and not full/exit counter. This class implements Serializable to allow objects of this class to be serialized.
